    {{#> base-section
        title="Qure’s Micro-Infusion goes where your skin cream can’t…"
        wistia="a1pykz2tp0"
    }}
        <p>The patent-pending system uses tiny, almost painless, microneedles penetrate beyond the skin’s surface increasing serum absorption and delivering powerful active ingredients exactly where they’re needed!</p>
        <p><strong>How Qure refreshes your skin in 3 easy steps:</strong></p>
        <ul class="e-steps-list">
            <li>
                <strong>Stamp</strong>
                <p>Patented 24k gold needles create micro-channels.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Infuse</strong>
                <p>Clinically formulated serum flows directly into the dermis, not on top of it.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Renews</strong>
                <p>Helps skin look refreshed and visibly renewed.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    {{/base-section }}

